acceptOwnership().details: Only callable by the current nominee. Sets nominee back to zero address.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

set(address[],bool[]).details: Whether an account is included is based on the boolean value at its respective index in `included`. This function will only edit the inclusion of addresses in `accounts`. The length of `accounts` and `included` must match. Only callable by `owner()`.

params.included: Whether to include corresponding address in `accounts`

reset().notice: Removes every address from the set.

set(address[],bool[]).notice: Sets whether an address in `accounts` is included.
